attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: South Boston 3-family building for sale!! A great fix-and-flip, house hack, buy and hold! Desirable K Street address near Seaport, Broadway, retail, restaurant, transit and under 1 mile from Pleasure Bay and 0.2 miles to Medal of Honor park! 3 units up and down, each unit is a 1-bed 1-bath. Units #2 and #3 each have a bonus office space and private reach decks. Unit 1 has electric heat, unit 2 has gas boiler steam radiators, and unit 3 has an forced air unit inside the living room closet. High ceilings throughout, hardwood floors, full basement in great condition with conc. floor. Seller has limited information on the property. TAW tenants in unit 1 and 2, and rents way below market rate. Seller and seller's agent/facilitator make no guarantees or warranties. Buyer to perform all due diligence. Building is sold "AS-IS" Estate sale. GROUP SHOWINGS ONLY: THURSDAY March 21st 11:30-12:30am and SATURDAY 3/23 12-1:30pm // OFFERS DUE: Monday, 3/25 by 12 noon.
